{"type":"step-attempt","step":"request-review","sessionId":"c836e791-7cc4-49a3-bdc4-e703784b0a0a","outcome":{"verdict":"approve","findingsPath":"specrunner/changes/simple-rate-limit/request-review-result-001.md","error":null,"toolResult":{"ok":true,"verdict":"approve","findings":[{"severity":"medium","resolution":"fixable","file":"specrunner/changes/simple-rate-limit/request.md","title":"rate_limit_records.key の構成値が未定義","rationale":"`rate_limit_records.key` は `text UNIQUE` カラムだが、格納する値（例: `userId:createRequest` vs `orgId:createRequest`）が未定義。キーをorg単位にすると1ユーザーがorg全体の枠を枯渇させうる。テーブルに `organizationId` カラムがない設計から per-user キーが意図されると推測できるが、明示がない。"},{"severity":"low","resolution":"fixable","file":"specrunner/changes/simple-rate-limit/request.md","title":"`remaining` の計算式が未定義","rationale":"返り値 `{ allowed: boolean, remaining: number }` の `remaining` 計算式が未定義。`limit - count` か `Math.max(0, limit - count)` かで負値挙動が変わる。"},{"severity":"low","resolution":"fixable","file":"specrunner/changes/simple-rate-limit/request.md","title":"`submitRequestAction` がスコープ外である旨の明示がない","rationale":"`submitRequestAction` は冪等キーチェックを持つが、レート制限対象に含まれておらず「スコープ外」セクションにも記載がない。意図的な除外か不明確。"}]},"followUpAttempts":1,"transientRetryAttempts":0},"startedAt":"2026-06-18T03:17:28.749Z","endedAt":"2026-06-18T03:20:37.734Z"}
